    "1101914": {
        "Desc": "Go to Blackcliff Forge to search for clues",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Sooooo... anything strange been going on recently?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iron Shoulder",
                    "T": "...Excuse me? What's that supposed to mean, strange how?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uhhh... just... y'know, stuff that when it happens, you think to yourself: \"That was weird!\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iron Shoulder",
                    "T": "?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "I don't think we're going to get anywhere asking questions like that. Let's just take a look around."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "1101916": {
        "Desc": "Investigate the logs",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What's this? A diary?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "From the back, it looks like a ledger. But it seems they also use it as a site log."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "We don't know who wrote it, but it's interesting, don't you think? These newcomers... Who could have sent them?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You think they're suspicious?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Yes. Look, it says right there: one of them's already been promoted to team leader."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "At this rate, by the time the Qingxu Pool Redevelopment Plan is ready to roll, they'll be the technical backbone of the team."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "That'll give them the chance to take a lot of liberties... They can copy any secret texts or steal any treasure they find underground."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Imagine if we didn't suspect anything. By the time Zhiyi recommends the Blackcliff Forge for the excavation project, at most we would maybe do a fresh background check on the place."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "No red flags if all they did was change some key staff. And even if we decided to vet the staff individually, they'd have had more than enough time by then to come up with fake identities."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "That's the advantage of planning this far in advance... It was a clever move."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "When you put it like that, it all makes sense... If we hadn't found this out, someone else would've stolen the treasure!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So who's really behind all this?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "That's a question for the newcomers. But let's start with that worker over there for now."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "1101915": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Iron Shoulder about the newcomers at the forge",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uh, excuse us... We wanna ask you about the newcomers!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iron Shoulder",
                    "T": "*sigh* You want them to teach you or something?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iron Shoulder",
                    "T": "I gotta say, these newcomers are in tip-top shape. Fast learners, too. They're picking up all the skills unbelievably fast."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iron Shoulder",
                    "T": "My only complaint is that they're always going out drinking at night, but they never let us join them."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iron Shoulder",
                    "T": "I guess they just need some time to adjust. I'm sure we'll get to know each other over time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "They go out drinking? This area isn't exactly renowned for the nightlife. I'm guessing it's a long trip to the nearest tavern?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iron Shoulder",
                    "T": "You got that right. They tell me they go all the way back to Liyue Harbor to drink at Wanmin Restaurant."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iron Shoulder",
                    "T": "It rained after work today, so they actually stuck around at the site for a while. But as soon as the rain stopped, they went out drinking again right away."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iron Shoulder",
                    "T": "Hey, you're only young once, right? I say, if they can hack it, let 'em at it, haha."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "#Interesting. Let's go talk somewhere else, {NICKNAME}."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Yelan takes you to a quieter place..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Looks like our hunch was on the Mora. These newcomers are very suspicious."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Drinking in Liyue Harbor, huh? Some cover story. I'll wager they've been going to intelligence updates..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Good thing it rained today — it means they'll leave footprints... I doubt they'd give themselves away that easily, but let's follow them and try our luck."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
