    "1101924": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Yelan",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Looks like we were too late."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "This has gotta be where the newcomers rendezvous with whoever they're working for. But all the evidence has been destroyed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Look at these ashes. Someone was burning documents not long before we arrived."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Could there be anything left? Maybe the wind could've blown the fire out before everything was finished burning?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "The odds of that are very slim. It's practically impossible. I've checked — all the paper's been burned. There's only ash left now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Why don't we wait for them back at the Blackcliff Forge? They've gotta go back there sooner or later."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "We can't count on that. Clearly, they were based here at one point, but it's mysteriously abandoned now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "To me, that says that whoever's behind this has moved them somewhere else to throw our investigation off course."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Darn... Guess this is where our trail runs cold!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Make no mistake, the purpose of our trip wasn't to find any solid evidence. We just need to figure out who's behind Zhiyi."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "I smelled something peculiar the moment I came in."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Those newcomers probably thought they'd be safe as long as they burned the letters. But what they failed to consider is that paper and ink from different regions produce different odors when they're burned."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Really? *sniff* Paimon can't smell anything! Do you smell anything, {NICKNAME}?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I smell a very gentle fragrance."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "There is a certain place with a freezing-cold climate where there's nothing but ice as far as the eye can see."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Some wealthy people there put floral fragrance in their ink as a way of injecting a little romance into their writing."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "When that fragrant ink is burned, this is the exact odor that it leaves behind..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Snezhnaya..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "The Fatui!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Exactly. The evidence will soon be blown away by the wind, so it's nothing we can arrest anyone with."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "But it's all I need. Now I know who we're dealing with, I can plan our next move."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "You leave the abandoned house with Yelan..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wupei",
                    "T": "Lady Yelan! Oh, thank goodness I finally found you! *sob* ...I thought I'd never see you again!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "...Um, who are you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Don't be alarmed, this is Wupei. He's Wenyuan and Shanghua's colleague."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "I sent him to look into Zhiyi's regular contacts. Since Zhiyi likes fishing, Wupei thought he might know some of the fishermen and sailors, so he took a boat out to sea to ask around."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "I left him a note at Yanshang Teahouse telling him to look for me at Blackcliff Forge when he got back. If there'd been an ambush waiting for us there, it means we'd have had some backup."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "So, what did you find out at sea?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wupei",
                    "T": "*sigh* Forgive my incompetence. I'm afraid I've come up empty-handed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wupei",
                    "T": "I asked all the fishermen multiple times, but none of them had had any interactions with Zhiyi before. Then the waves got so choppy I ended up falling overboard. Fortunately, someone managed to drag me out."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wupei",
                    "T": "When I got back, I heard that you'd gone to Blackcliff Forge and might need backup, so I went straight there as fast as I could. Didn't even stop to change my clothes."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Oh? Well, Uncle Tian said that Zhiyi once bought a recipe from one of the fishermen. Did you hear anything about that at all?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wupei",
                    "T": "What? That's news to me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wupei",
                    "T": "No, that's not possible... It's absolutely not possible! Lady Yelan, I'm telling you — I spoke to every single fisherman out there, and none of them mentioned anything about a recipe."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Interesting... Then I wonder how that \"even more wonderful\" fish soup came about?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wupei",
                    "T": "Fish soup? What fish soup?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Nothing. Our priority right now is to find a way to get our hands on some solid evidence."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Well, any suggestions?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Send someone to tail them?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Catch them red-handed when they meet..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Not a bad idea. Wupei, what do you think?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wupei",
                    "T": "Honestly, I've already tried following Zhiyi. But the guy's too cautious. Never meets with anyone suspicious."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Okay, so tailing's out..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "No, we'll still need to tail him. But first, we need to do some groundwork."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Groundwork?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "When you've worked in intelligence for a long time, you'll understand that no one can stay on high alert forever. Especially... when he thinks he's about to win."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Tomorrow morning, I'll announce his victory at Yuehai Pavillion. Take a guess, what do you think he'll do next?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Be sure to arrive on time. You won't wanna miss the show."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
