    "1102615": {
        "Desc": "Follow Yelan",
        "Step": "To think that Zhiyi was in such a hurry to silence Yusupov tonight... Well, now that that mess is over, it is time to clean up.",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "I did a little surveying on the way here, and found that you'd left yourself three escape routes in case things went south."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "I have them all surrounded. If you're thinking of trying anything, save yourself the effort. The game's up."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "We were here the whole time and have pictures of everything. They came out pretty nicely, wanna see them?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiyi",
                    "T": "\"The game's up\"? ...Forgive me, I'm not quite sure what you're referring to, Ms. Yelan?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiyi",
                    "T": "I happened to discover a Fatui operation here, so I approached them on the pretext of joining forces and eventually brought them down from within. If it pleases you, Ms. Yelan, I'd be only too happy to have you join me in investigating this matter."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "This is how you want to play it, huh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Fine, you do you. All we need to do to convict you is establish that the poison in his system is the same as in Uncle Tian's."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiyi",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Nothing else you wanted to add? Let's leave it there then. Time to go."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiyi",
                    "T": "One wrong move and it all comes crashing down... I should have been more careful."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiyi",
                    "T": "You followed him here, didn't you? I was so focused on keeping myself out of sight, I forgot he was a potential liability."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiyi",
                    "T": "Let's talk about this, Yelan. I gave you my word that I would live up to the Tianshu name, and that much I can still guarantee."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Your point being?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiyi",
                    "T": "When I take office, I can guarantee that I will act in your best interests. In fact, all of you here tonight can expect very generous treatment in the future."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiyi",
                    "T": "I don't deny that I used underhanded methods to get here. But given my lowly origins, what other choice did I have?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Hmph, you still don't get it, do you? Even now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "#What do you think, {NICKNAME}?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What will Uncle Tian think?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Uncle Tian has always trusted you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Exactly. Zhiyi, clever people can always come up with a good excuse. But while you might be able to get other people to believe you, you'll never be able to deceive yourself."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "There's nothing wrong with wanting to win other people's respect. But when has Uncle Tian ever looked down on you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "He was like a teacher and a father to you, but you chose to repay that by poisoning him... Whatever positive goal you may have started out with, you threw it away in that moment."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiyi",
                    "T": "That's enough... I..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Of course, what makes this even crueler is that you managed to convince yourself there was \"no other way.\" Uncle Tian was always going to give you this opportunity... even if you'd done nothing at all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Out of everyone in the world, he is the one who trusts you the most. So much that he drank your fish soup without doubting you, not for one second."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Zhiyi",
                    "T": "That's enough! ...That's enough."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "#Sorry, things are about to get extremely busy for me. Let's meet at Yanshang Teahouse tomorrow morning, {NICKNAME}."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "I'll have someone remove the explosives. Then, there's someone I have to go and see."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Need our help with that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "No. It could be dangerous... You should leave this one to the professionals."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Be careful."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Don't worry. As long as they're willing to cooperate, this'll be a straightforward deal."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Get some rest. See you tomorrow."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
